OL,3,CLandmark equal pay deal for Birmingham
OL,4,CCity Council
OL,6,FBirmingham City Council has signed a
OL,7,Fformal agreement with trade unions
OL,8,FUNISON and GMB to settle outstanding
OL,9,Fequal pay claims, marking a major step
OL,10,Fin resolving one of the most costly
OL,11,Fdisputes in the council's history.
OL,13,FThe framework agreement, which follows
OL,14,Fa deal reached in principle last
OL,15,FDecember and later approved by the
OL,16,Fcouncil's cabinet, covers claims
OL,17,Fbrought on behalf of members working
OL,18,Ffor both the local authority and
OL,19,FBirmingham Children's Trust.
