OL,3,CLandmark equal pay deal for Birmingham
OL,4,CCity Council
OL,6,FCouncil leader Cllr John Cotton said:
OL,7,F"When I was appointed as Leader two
OL,8,Fyears ago, I labelled equal pay the
OL,9,Fsingle biggest challenge that the
OL,10,Fcouncil has faced and vowed to deal
OL,11,Fwith the matter once and for all.
OL,13,F"We're doing exactly that and this
OL,14,Fdeal represents another key milestone
OL,15,Fon our journey. I want to thank GMB
OL,16,Fand UNISON for working so
OL,17,Fconstructively with the council to put
OL,18,Fright a historic wrong."
