OL,6,FThe full terms of the settlement
OL,7,Fremain confidential, but in a
OL,8,Fstatement the council acknowledged
OL,9,Fthat previous administrations had
OL,10,Ffailed to act decisively enough on
OL,11,Fequal pay concerns, saying those
OL,12,Fshortcomings had "a lasting impact on
OL,13,Four workforce and the trust placed in
OL,14,Fus by the people of Birmingham."
OL,26,@tD@ROUvD@`O]
