OL,6,FIt continued: "We recognise that
OL,7,Fprevious custodians of the council did
OL,8,Fnot act swiftly or decisively enough
OL,9,Fto resolve these matters. As the
OL,10,Fcurrent leadership, we are committed
OL,11,Fto learning from these mistakes and
OL,12,Fensuring they are not repeated."
OL,14,FThe council said it is working closely
OL,15,Fwith trade unions to ensure fairness
OL,16,Fin pay and job evaluation going
OL,17,Fforward, adding that the new framework
OL,18,Faims to avoid further litigation and
OL,19,F"move forward with a fairer, more
OL,20,Ftransparent job evaluation scheme and
OL,21,Fpay structure."
