OL,6,F"We will now be focused on getting
OL,7,Fmoney back where it belongs, into the
OL,8,Fpockets of our members as a matter of
OL,9,Furgency."
OL,11,FClaire Campbell, UNISON regional
OL,12,Fmanager, said: "This agreement marks a
OL,13,Fturning point for hundreds of low-paid
OL,14,Fwomen who have waited far too long for
OL,15,Fjustice and equal pay. It's a
OL,16,Ftestament to their strength,
OL,17,Fresilience and to the power of
OL,18,Fcollective action.
