OL,6,F"UNISON is now focused on ensuring
OL,7,Fthese payments reach staff as quickly
OL,8,Fas possible."
OL,10,FLead commissioner Tony McArdle said
OL,11,Fthe deal was a positive step for the
OL,12,Fcouncil's future. "The failure to
OL,13,Fresolve Equal Pay over many years has
OL,14,Fcost the council dearly," he said.
