OL,4,CCity Council
OL,6,F"This agreement presents a real
OL,7,Fopportunity for the Council to limit
OL,8,Ffurther costs and to positively reset
OL,9,Fits relationship with its staff and
OL,10,Ftrade unions. It's an encouraging step
OL,11,Fforward and one as commissioners we
OL,12,Fare pleased to see the council make."
OL,14,FThe council said it would continue to
OL,15,Freview its job evaluation processes
OL,16,Fregularly and strengthen governance
OL,17,Fstructures to maintain fairness and
OL,18,Ftransparency across all roles.
